{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_51_03",
  "title": "白石千紗 3話 自慢の妹だから",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――本番が迫ったある日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――One day‚ with the live date fast approaching.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "1、2、3、4……1、2、3、4……\nはぁ、はぁ……まだクセで動きが小さくなっちゃう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "One‚ two‚ three‚ four… one‚ two‚ three‚ four…\nHuff‚ huff… My movements are still too small out of habit…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.1831462644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "一人でステージに立つんだから……\nもっと、大きく……ステージも広く使って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since I’m standing on stage alone…\nI need to be… bigger… use the whole stage…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.4666666746,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4199.999992100001,
          "startTime": 20.6666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4699.999992100001,
          "startTime": 21.1666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃん、お疲れ様\nはい、これ。差し入れに、ドリンク買ってきたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa-chan‚ good work.\nHere. I bought you some drinks as a treat.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.7666665474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ～、これ私が好きなやつだ。でも、二本もいいの？\nもしかして、イマジナリーSISTERの分……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow~‚ this is my favorite. But are you sure I can have both?\nIs it for… my Imaginary Sister…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.233333214,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "違うよ。ただ……千紗ちゃんのことを応援してるのは\n私だけじゃないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No. It’s just… I'm not the only one\nwho’s cheering for you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.233333214,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "……？　あっ、でもそうだよね。マネージャーさん達や\n星見プロのみんなも、楽しみにしてくれてるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…? Oh‚ right. The managers and\neveryone at Hoshimi Pro are looking forward to it too‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.2999998807,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "……本当はね、まだ……怖い気持ちもあるんだ……\n本番が近づくほど、不安で、焦って、ドキドキして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…To be honest‚ I’m still… a little scared…\nThe closer it gets to the live‚ the more anxious‚ impatient‚ and nervous I get…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.566665268,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "本番で失敗しちゃうかも……歌えないかもって……\n何度も何度も、頭に浮かんじゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What if I mess up at the show…? What if I can’t sing…?\nThose thoughts keep popping into my head…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.5000044584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.6333377917,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、応援してくれる人がいるから……\nこんな私のために……私、一人だけのライブなのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But there are people cheering for me…\nFor me… even though it’s just my own live show…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.2000044584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "それでも、来たいって……絶対に行く、頑張れって\nファンの人達が、SNSで書いてくれてて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They still… want to come… and they cheer me on.\nMy fans write those things on social media.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.7666711251,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "だから、頑張りたい。今、私が出来る精一杯……\nううん、それ以上のライブが出来るように",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I want to do my best. I want to put on the best show I can right now…\nNo‚ I want to put on a show that surpasses that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.2000044584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "みんなに、届くように",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want it to reach everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.3333291451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "……届くよ、絶対",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It will reach them‚ definitely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.7333367745,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3633.329510699994,
          "startTime": 118.3666662852
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 117.9833367745
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃん、もう少しだけ残っていくって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa-chan said she was going to stay and practice a little longer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.0333367745,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます\n差し入れ、持っていってくれて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you.\nFor bringing her a treat.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.7666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "うん、喜んでたよ\nでも、沙季ちゃんから渡した方が良かったんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ she was happy about it.\nBut it's been better if you had given it to her‚ Saki-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.6790052175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃんから、忙しいって聞いてたけど……\n練習を覗いたりして……本当は、心配なんだよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa-chan said you were busy‚ but…\nYou peeked into her practice… You’re worried about her‚ aren’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.2456718842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃんも、不安そうだったし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa-chan seemed anxious too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.3790052175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "……千紗は、もう、一人で走れるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Chisa… can run on her own now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.1456718842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "……え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.2579969644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "白石千紗はBIG4の一角、サニーピースのメンバーで\n立派な一人のアイドルなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa Shiraishi is a member of BIG4‚ and Sunny Peace‚\nand a fine idol in her own right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.3999853769,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "歌もダンスも、昔よりずっとうまくなってる\n伝えたい想いだって、しっかりと持ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Her singing and dancing have improved a lot since before‚\nand she has her own thoughts and feelings she wants to convey.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.1666520435,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "それだけサニーピースで……星見プロで努力して\n成長してきたことを、私は誰よりも知っています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know better than anyone how much she’s worked hard\nand grown in Sunny Peace… in Hoshimi Productions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.7666520435,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "だから、大丈夫です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So it’s okay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.7075370072,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "むしろそばにいたら\n私の方が、つい過保護になっちゃいますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If anything‚ if I’m by her side‚\nI’ll just end up being overprotective.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.3999813078,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "沙季ちゃん……。ふふ、そうかもね\nそういえば、本当にライブ、観に来れないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki-chan… Fufu‚ maybe you’re right.\nSpeaking of which‚ can you really not come to see the live show?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.7546306529,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね、予定がありますから\n頼んで入れてもらった、大切な予定が",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I have plans.\nI have… important plans that I asked them to schedule for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.1999813078,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5570.011925800003,
          "startTime": 198.7699932336
        }
      ]
