      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehhh!? Saki-chan!?\nWhy!? You said you had plans today…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 323.2266063928,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-night",
      "startTime": 327.1932974736
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_03-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、大事な予定があったわ\n千紗のライブにこうして出させてもらうっていう予定が",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I had important plans.\nPlans to appear at Chisa’s live show.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 329.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
